SentClaimServiceLineFact

The sent claim service line fact contains information about procedures from claims sent from an accounts receivable (A/R) system.

For Resolute Hospital Billing, Resolute Professional Billing, and Healthy Planet 837 external professional claims loaded from Clarity, each row represents a service line from a sent claim. For Healthy Planet 837 external institutional claims loaded from Clarity, each row represents either a service line or a procedure from the claim header.

Properties

Reporting table name
dbo.SentClaimServiceLineFact
Granularity
A procedure or service line reported on a sent claim
